":index:`When the ripper log file is available <workflows; ripper log, "
"lookup; ripper log, EAC; lookup log, XLD; lookup log, Whipper; lookup log, "
"fre:ac; lookup log, dBpoweramp; lookup log>`"
msgstr ""
